What a great icon pack, the best I've seen so far, and the one I want to use on all of my devices. This app allows you to leave any particular icon as is, or choose from over 1300 ready made smoke & glass icons within the pack, and what makes this icon pack extra special, is the ability to give any system or 3rd party app icons an instant smoke & glass makeover which makes pages full of icons look bang tidy. As for the look of these icons, they really do look like smokey glass spheres, a cool look as well as pleasing on the eye. I'm not keen on paying for icons as they're ten a penny (an old English saying for cheap), but this icon pack set me back a penny under 1 and a half quid, well and truly worth the money. Definitely a five star app, congrats and thanks to the developer.
